==English==
=== Etymology ===

From the Chinese word 泡沫, which is in turn derived phonetically from the English word ''[[bubble]]''.

=== Noun ===
'''boba''' (pl. ''uncountable'')

# Small, usually black, balls of [[tapioca]] used in beverages, which are generally consumed through a large straw.
# A beverage containing these balls of tapioca.

